  "success": true,
  "message": "Categories retrieved successfully",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "33a1b2c3-1111-2222-3333-444455556666",
      "name": "Plumbing",
      "description": "Pipe leakage, sink installation, and sanitary works"
    },
    {
      "id": "44b2c3d4-2222-3333-4444-555566667777",
      "name": "Electrical",
      "description": "Wiring, switchboard repair, appliance installation"
    }
  ]
}
```

Retrieve all bookings placed by the authenticated customer. Every booking object explicitly includes `bookingId` alongside `id` to eliminate ID confusion during payment or tracking.

### Sample Success Response (`200 OK`):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Bookings retrieved successfully",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "3624ffb7-3013-42f6-9381-909770ac9b67",
      "bookingId": "3624ffb7-3013-42f6-9381-909770ac9b67",
      "status": "REQUESTED",
      "totalPrice": 49.99,
      "bookingDate": "2026-07-20T10:00:00.000Z",
      "service": {
        "title": "Pipe Leakage Repair & Replacement"
      },
      "technician": {
        "name": "Devid Technician",
        "phone": "+8801711111111"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Verify/confirm a completed Stripe transaction. Updates the payment record `status` to `COMPLETED` and advances the booking `status` to `PAID`.

### Request Body Schema:
```json
{
  "transactionId": "cs_test_a1a4J6V2orMNqPwgy43UtNg19hDk4zEXJMCE5Ag2KjVspO3pjjuWwpu2VL"
}
```

### Sample Success Response (`200 OK`):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Payment confirmed and booking marked as PAID",
  "data": {
    "id": "cdb1d39c-bae6-40af-bbda-60f61e1369a2",
    "transactionId": "cs_test_a1a4J6V2orMNqPwgy43UtNg19hDk4zEXJMCE5Ag2KjVspO3pjjuWwpu2VL",
    "status": "COMPLETED",
    "paidAt": "2026-07-09T10:30:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

