request.description:
Ban or unban a user. When `isBanned: true`, the user is blocked from logging in or performing actions across FixItNow.

### Request Body Schema (`true` to ban, `false` to unban):
```json
{
  "isBanned": true
}
```

### Sample Success Response (`200 OK`):
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User status updated successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": "e4cfac41-a357-4bd6-b1ad-521b831c9f6f",
    "name": "Evan Customer",
    "isBanned": true
  }
}
```

